{"word":"ὑπερκάθημαι","slug":"ὑπερκάθημαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπερκάθημαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>properly <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> of <el>-έζομαι</el>\n<p/><i>to sit over</i> or <i>upon</i>, <el>ἐπί τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to sit over and watch, keep an eye on</i>, <el>τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}